{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1713,"text":"Can I get a show of hands --"},{"time":3103,"text":"how many of you in this room\nhave been on a plane in this past year?"},{"time":8258,"text":"That's pretty good."},{"time":9435,"text":"Well, it turns out that you\nshare that experience"},{"time":12344,"text":"with more than three billion\npeople every year."},{"time":15203,"text":"And when we put so many people\nin all these metal tubes"},{"time":18364,"text":"that fly all over the world,"},{"time":19974,"text":"sometimes, things like this can happen"},{"time":22671,"text":"and you get a disease epidemic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25116,"text":"I first actually got into this topic"},{"time":27091,"text":"when I heard about the Ebola\noutbreak last year."},{"time":29747,"text":"And it turns out that,"},{"time":31231,"text":"although Ebola spreads\nthrough these more range-limited,"},{"time":34085,"text":"large-droplet routes,"},{"time":35443,"text":"there's all these other sorts of diseases"},{"time":37445,"text":"that can be spread in the airplane cabin."},{"time":39445,"text":"The worst part is, when we take\na look at some of the numbers,"},{"time":42653,"text":"it's pretty scary."},{"time":44090,"text":"So with H1N1,"},{"time":45874,"text":"there was this guy that decided\nto go on the plane"},{"time":48287,"text":"and in the matter of a single flight"},{"time":50082,"text":"actually spread the disease\nto 17 other people."},{"time":52360,"text":"And then there was this\nother guy with SARS,"},{"time":54512,"text":"who managed to go on a three-hour flight"},{"time":56638,"text":"and spread the disease to 22 other people."},{"time":59504,"text":"That's not exactly my idea\nof a great superpower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63658,"text":"When we take a look at this,\nwhat we also find"},{"time":66246,"text":"is that it's very difficult\nto pre-screen for these diseases."},{"time":69619,"text":"So when someone actually\ngoes on a plane,"},{"time":71734,"text":"they could be sick"},{"time":72964,"text":"and they could actually\nbe in this latency period"},{"time":75383,"text":"in which they could actually\nhave the disease"},{"time":77566,"text":"but not exhibit any symptoms,"},{"time":79162,"text":"and they could, in turn,\nspread the disease"},{"time":81377,"text":"to many other people in the cabin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83074,"text":"How that actually works is that right now"},{"time":85180,"text":"we've got air coming in\nfrom the top of the cabin"},{"time":87490,"text":"and from the side of the cabin,\nas you see in blue."},{"time":89940,"text":"And then also, that air goes out\nthrough these very efficient filters"},{"time":94166,"text":"that eliminate 99.97 percent\nof pathogens near the outlets."},{"time":99444,"text":"What happens right now, though,"},{"time":100945,"text":"is that we have this\nmixing airflow pattern."},{"time":103036,"text":"So if someone were to actually sneeze,"},{"time":104892,"text":"that air would get swirled\naround multiple times"},{"time":107620,"text":"before it even has a chance\nto go out through the filter."},{"time":111785,"text":"So I thought: clearly, this\nis a pretty serious problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115022,"text":"I didn't have the money\nto go out and buy a plane,"},{"time":118779,"text":"so I decided to build a computer instead."},{"time":121041,"text":"It actually turns out that\nwith computational fluid dynamics,"},{"time":124337,"text":"what we're able to do\nis create these simulations"},{"time":126962,"text":"that give us higher resolutions"},{"time":128780,"text":"than actually physically going\nin and taking readings in the plane."},{"time":132836,"text":"And so how, essentially, this works\nis you would start out"},{"time":135874,"text":"with these 2D drawings --"},{"time":137570,"text":"these are floating around\nin technical papers around the Internet."},{"time":140722,"text":"I take that and then I put it\ninto this 3D-modeling software,"},{"time":143639,"text":"really building that 3D model."},{"time":145442,"text":"And then I divide that model\nthat I just built into these tiny pieces,"},{"time":149925,"text":"essentially meshing it so that\nthe computer can better understand it."},{"time":153526,"text":"And then I tell the computer where\nthe air goes in and out of the cabin,"},{"time":157271,"text":"throw in a bunch of physics"},{"time":158794,"text":"and basically sit there and wait until\nthe computer calculates the simulation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164015,"text":"So what we get, actually,\nwith the conventional cabin is this:"},{"time":167666,"text":"you'll notice the middle person sneezing,"},{"time":170767,"text":"and we go \"Splat!\" -- it goes\nright into people's faces."},{"time":174882,"text":"It's pretty disgusting."},{"time":176727,"text":"From the front, you'll notice\nthose two passengers"},{"time":179099,"text":"sitting next to the central passenger"},{"time":180909,"text":"not exactly having a great time."},{"time":182639,"text":"And when we take a look\nat that from the side,"},{"time":184849,"text":"you'll also notice those pathogens\nspreading across the length of the cabin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190017,"text":"The first thing I thought was,\n\"This is no good.\""},{"time":192391,"text":"So I actually conducted\nmore than 32 different simulations"},{"time":195923,"text":"and ultimately, I came up\nwith this solution right here."},{"time":199312,"text":"This is what I call a -- patent pending --\nGlobal Inlet Director."},{"time":202852,"text":"With this, we're able to reduce\npathogen transmission"},{"time":205442,"text":"by about 55 times,"},{"time":207234,"text":"and increase fresh-air inhalation\nby about 190 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210411,"text":"So how this actually works"},{"time":212039,"text":"is we would install this piece\nof composite material"},{"time":215192,"text":"into these existing spots\nthat are already in the plane."},{"time":218184,"text":"So it's very cost-effective to install"},{"time":220209,"text":"and we can do this directly overnight."},{"time":222081,"text":"All we have to do is put a couple\nof screws in there and you're good to go."},{"time":225653,"text":"And the results that we get\nare absolutely amazing."},{"time":228536,"text":"Instead of having those problematic\nswirling airflow patterns,"},{"time":232096,"text":"we can create these walls of air"},{"time":233862,"text":"that come down in-between the passengers"},{"time":236056,"text":"to create personalized breathing zones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237978,"text":"So you'll notice the middle passenger\nhere is sneezing again,"},{"time":240987,"text":"but this time, we're able\nto effectively push that down"},{"time":243724,"text":"to the filters for elimination."},{"time":246461,"text":"And same thing from the side,"},{"time":247881,"text":"you'll notice we're able to directly\npush those pathogens down."},{"time":251682,"text":"So if you take a look again now\nat the same scenario"},{"time":255200,"text":"but with this innovation installed,"},{"time":256913,"text":"you'll notice the middle\npassenger sneezes,"},{"time":258953,"text":"and this time, we're pushing\nthat straight down into the outlet"},{"time":262050,"text":"before it gets a chance\nto infect any other people."},{"time":265795,"text":"So you'll notice the two passengers\nsitting next to the middle guy"},{"time":268943,"text":"are breathing virtually\nno pathogens at all."},{"time":271200,"text":"Take a look at that from the side as well,"},{"time":273752,"text":"you see a very efficient system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275331,"text":"And in short, with this system, we win."},{"time":279255,"text":"When we take a look at what this means,"},{"time":282168,"text":"what we see is that this not only works\nif the middle passenger sneezes,"},{"time":285664,"text":"but also if the window-seat\npassenger sneezes"},{"time":288462,"text":"or if the aisle-seat passenger sneezes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291167,"text":"And so with this solution, what does\nthis mean for the world?"},{"time":294278,"text":"Well, when we take a look at this"},{"time":297816,"text":"from the computer simulation\ninto real life,"},{"time":300409,"text":"we can see with this 3D model\nthat I built over here,"},{"time":303195,"text":"essentially using 3D printing,"},{"time":305307,"text":"we can see those same\nairflow patterns coming down,"},{"time":308290,"text":"right to the passengers."},{"time":310920,"text":"In the past, the SARS epidemic\nactually cost the world"},{"time":314014,"text":"about 40 billion dollars."},{"time":315967,"text":"And in the future,"},{"time":317150,"text":"a big disease outbreak\ncould actually cost the world"},{"time":319720,"text":"in excess of three trillion dollars."},{"time":321942,"text":"So before, it used to be that you had\nto take an airplane out of service"},{"time":325443,"text":"for one to two months,"},{"time":327339,"text":"spend tens of thousands of man hours\nand several million dollars"},{"time":330935,"text":"to try to change something."},{"time":332282,"text":"But now, we're able to install\nsomething essentially overnight"},{"time":335817,"text":"and see results right away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337568,"text":"So it's really now a matter of taking\nthis through to certification,"},{"time":340798,"text":"flight testing,"},{"time":342012,"text":"and going through all of these\nregulatory approvals processes."},{"time":345028,"text":"But it just really goes to show\nthat sometimes the best solutions"},{"time":348116,"text":"are the simplest solutions."},{"time":349935,"text":"And two years ago, even,"},{"time":353149,"text":"this project would not have happened,"},{"time":354942,"text":"just because the technology then\nwouldn't have supported it."},{"time":357792,"text":"But now with advanced computing"},{"time":360285,"text":"and how developed our Internet is,"},{"time":362495,"text":"it's really the golden era for innovation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365158,"text":"And so the question I ask all\nof you today is: why wait?"},{"time":368425,"text":"Together, we can build the future today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371123,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372298,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}